fields.name: linked_domains

fields.description: The number of unique domains linked from your target with followed links.

fields.name: org_cost
fields.description: (10 units) The estimated value of your target’s monthly organic search traffic.

fields.name: org_keywords
fields.description: The total number of keywords that your target ranks for in the top 100 organic search results. When ranking for the same keyword across different locations in “All locations” mode, it's still counted as one keyword.

fields.name: org_keywords_11_20
fields.description: The total number of unique keywords for which your target's top organic ranking position is within the 11th to 20th results. When ranking for the same keyword across different locations in “All locations” mode, it's still counted as one keyword.

fields.name: org_keywords_1_3
fields.description: The total number of unique keywords for which your target's top organic ranking position is within the top 3 results. When ranking for the same keyword across different locations in “All locations” mode, it's still counted as one keyword.

fields.name: org_keywords_21_50
fields.description: The total number of unique keywords for which your target's top organic ranking position is within the 21st to 50th results. When ranking for the same keyword across different locations in “All locations” mode, it's still counted as one keyword.

fields.name: org_keywords_4_10
fields.description: The total number of unique keywords for which your target's top organic ranking position is within the 4th to 10th results. When ranking for the same keyword across different locations in “All locations” mode, it's still counted as one keyword.

fields.name: org_keywords_51_plus
fields.description: The total number of unique keywords for which your target's top organic ranking position is the 51st result or higher. When ranking for the same keyword across different locations in “All locations” mode, it's still counted as one keyword.

fields.name: org_traffic
fields.description: (10 units) The estimated number of monthly visits that your target gets from organic search.

fields.name: org_traffic_top_by_country
fields.description: (10 units) Top countries by traffic with corresponding traffic values. (Currently only a single element is being returned with the country with the most traffic.)

fields.name: outgoing_links
fields.description: The total number of links from your target to other domains.

fields.name: outgoing_links_dofollow
fields.description: The total number of followed links from your target to other domains.

fields.name: paid_ads
fields.description: The total number of unique ads of a target website or URL in paid search results.

fields.name: paid_cost
fields.description: (10 units) The estimated cost of your target’s monthly paid search traffic.

fields.name: paid_keywords
fields.description: The total number of keywords that your target ranks for in paid search results. When ranking for the same keyword across different locations in “All locations” mode, it's still counted as one keyword.

fields.name: paid_traffic
fields.description: (10 units) The estimated number of monthly visits that your target gets from paid search.

fields.name: protocol

fields.name: refdomains
fields.description: (5 units) The total number of unique domains linking to your target.

fields.name: refdomains_dofollow

fields.name: refdomains_nofollow

fields.name: refips

fields.name: refips_subnets
fields.description: The number of c-class IP networks (AAA.BBB.CCC.DDD) with at least one link to your target. Example: 151.80.39.61 is the website IP address where 151.80.39.XXX is the subnet.

fields.name: url
